From Lance Visser Subject Re Welcome to Police State USA In Very Old Freshman VOF writes Critisism is too What solutions do people have that would have been better than what the FBI had been doing for the last few months After the seige began Surround the place with Razor wire and then let them Do not have daily press conferences do your best to keep things out of the As things get more and more miserable inside one of two things is going to happen People will start coming They will commit suicide in mass at some The thing to remember about is that hysterical situations and assults play into the hands of a leader who has picked this Its much easier to stampede people into something like suicide if there is gas coming in and bullets in the Let them be hungry and miserable for longer and longer and it will probably be more The possiblity that they would all kill themselves at some point would not bother me in the least or alter If people are going to take their own lives the best you can probably do is prevent yourself from giving them the opportunity or an excuse to do If the FBI and Attorney General Vampira really were concerned with sanitation and welfare of the children inside they would not have turned the water to the compound off as a pressure tactic in the first